 its unflinching commitment to the protection of lives and property in the Federal Capital Territory.” Vanguard News Nigeria The reportedly drunk policeman caught on camera around Akowonjo, Dopemu area of Lagos State, was dismissed by the Police authorities yesterday. November 8, 2018 In "Crime Guard" The Commissioner of Police FCT, CP Bala Ciroma, has ordered a discreet investigation into an unfortunate gunshot incident that led to the death of one Solomon Eze, 52 years old at Karimo on Sunday 10th May 2020 at about 6:00 pm. May 11, 2020 In "News" A woman who was seen in a video that went viral on social media, slapping a policeman, in Oyo State, has been arrested. May 3, 2020 In "News"